QuestData.Title: Revival Catalyst
QuestData.Description:
The catalyst is a powerful artifact capable of great feats of empowerment.
As you go forth with your allies and give battle to the greater threats of this land, bring back any Renascence you find. With it, we can power the catalyst to imbue your equipment with the wisdom and might of Tyr himself.
QuestData.LogDescription: Gather Renascence from group content throughout the Dragon Isles.

Objectives.Objective: Complete Group Content on the Dragon Isles
